Sentencas: La0.84Sr0.16MnO3-delta - Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (LSM-GDC) composite cathodes were fabricated by impregnating the LSM matrix with both LSM' (La0.84Sr0.16MnO3-delta) and GDC (or only GDC), and the ion-impregnated LSM-GDC composite cathodes showed excellent performance.
Titulo: Improvement of a GDC-based composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 750 A degrees C, the value of the cathode polarization resistance (R (p) ) was only 0.058 Omega cm(2) for an ion-impregnated LSM-GDC composite cathode which was impregnated with both LSM' and GDC.
Titulo: Improvement of a GDC-based composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For the performance of the single cell with the same cathode, the maximum power density was 1.1 W cm(-2) at 750 A degrees C.
Titulo: Improvement of a GDC-based composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The long-term test of the cell was carried out at 700 A degrees C with a constant load of 0.3 A cm(-2) and the output voltage was stable on the whole.
Titulo: Improvement of a GDC-based composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results demonstrated that LSM-GDC fabricated by impregnating the LSM matrix with both LSM' and GDC was a promising composite cathode material for the intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Improvement of a GDC-based composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
